[Cheats\2 OPTIONAL - Universal in-vehicle D-pad radio/look controls]
description=Requires group 1. All vehicles including Rhino: D-pad Up=next radio station/native D-pad Down, D-pad Left=look left/native L2, D-pad Right=look right/native R2, D-pad Down=look back/native L2+R2. This single module controls the in-vehicle D-pad/look/radio behavior.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

