description=Requires group 1. On foot only. Removes the old D-pad remaps. Shoulder swap: physical L1 outputs native L2; physical R1 outputs native R2; physical L2 outputs native L1; physical R2 outputs native R1.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

